{"tid":686330,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先係信和比人打=.=lll","createTime":"2018-06-01T07:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T05:56:55.000Z","uid":52073,"like":26,"dislike":324,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0a7a527cef0a07c4bc0aa10d7ae7aa30da0ccb","tid":686330,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"是咁的,頭先約左個動物台手足出去交收figure<br />\n<br />\n名我就唔開了 動物台知名會然黎<br />\n<br />\n約好左1點半係信和等,見到佢我就同佢打招呼啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後再拎盒figure比佢睇 點知佢一野拍跌我盒figure <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我緊係即刻發火問佢係咪想隻秋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢突然一腳踢落我個肚到 我比佢打到訓左係到-.- <br />\n<br />\n跟住佢仲搶左我盒figure走,我好嬲 覺得自己好冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都冇得罪你 點解你要咁對我.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過好彩盒figure係假野黎,我同你講 你下次再撞到我就死定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b37bd945afd08d1bfbed6e1258ca3a37998b7a","tid":686330,"uid":21423,"like":88,"dislike":43,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cedab59a8caab463a8275614b6fca7b09ed65b2","tid":686330,"uid":52073,"like":134,"dislike":5,"score":129,"quote":{"pid":"34b37bd945afd08d1bfbed6e1258ca3a37998b7a","tid":686330,"uid":21423,"like":88,"dislike":43,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:12:48.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"d44d9f4039127a0e388ae5637474b341958da760","tid":686330,"uid":31429,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:15:17.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"7c0b8025150d1dfb568ab6f2b5b74d174f0e18b1","tid":686330,"uid":189053,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:16:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"462029727fae3756849